Interface Path

All Known Subinterfaces:
DirectoryPath, FilePath
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDirectoryPath, FsDirectoryPath, FsFilePath, SimplePath, WebappDirectoryPath, WebappFilePath, ZipDirectoryPath, ZipEntryDirectoryPath, ZipEntryFilePath, ZipEntryPath, ZipFilePath
public interface Path

A path is an element which is could be linked to another path as parent to represent a hierarchy.
